                        <tr><td>Visit Details</td><td>Pages visited, time spent, referral source</td><td>Analyze usage patterns and improve content</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Geolocation Data</td><td>Approximate location derived from IP address</td><td>Content personalization and analytics</td></tr>
