                    <li><span class="highlight">Clicked Elements</span> - Buttons, links, or forms you interact with</li>
                    <li><span class="highlight">Scroll Behavior</span> - How far you scroll on our pages</li>
                    <li><span class="highlight">Time Spent</span> - Duration of your visit and engagement</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>2.3 Information You Provide</h3>
                <p>When you fill out forms on our website (such as the contact form), we may collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Contact information (name, email address)</li>
                    <li>Message content and inquiries</li>
                    <li>Any other details you voluntarily provide</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide and maintain our website services</li>
                    <li>Analyze usage patterns to improve user experience</li>
