                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2>4. Data Collection Technologies</h2>
                <p>We use the following methods to collect data:</p>
                <table class="data-table">
                    <thead><tr><th>Technology</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>JavaScript Tracking</td><td>Collects interaction data (clicks, scrolls, time spent)</td></tr>
